.SH NAME
octane-keywords-list - Print all registered keywords


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBoctane keywords list [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
list prints every keyword registered in the keyword registry,
sorted by layer (primitive then domain), OCPP version, and pattern.

.PP
Each line is formatted as:
  [] [] 


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for list


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
\fB--cache-dir\fP=""
	override the cache directory (default: $XDG_CACHE_HOME/octane/cache)

.PP
\fB--config\fP="octane.yml"
	path to octane.yml configuration file

.PP
\fB--no-cache\fP[=false]
	bypass the result cache entirely

.PP
\fB-v\fP, \fB--verbose\fP[=false]
	enable verbose output


